---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service | ROOKIE STUDIO" description="Terms of service for ROOKIE STUDIO web development and software solutions.">
  <Navbar />
  <main class="pt-32 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-display mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mb-12">Last updated: June 29, 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-8 text-text-secondary">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">1. Services</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">ROOKIE STUDIO provides web development, mobile app development, and custom software solutions. Services include but are not limited to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-4">
            <li>Website design and development</li>
            <li>Mobile application development</li>
            <li>Custom software and dashboard creation</li>
            <li>UI/UX design services</li>
            <li>Ongoing maintenance and support</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">2. Payment Terms</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Landing Page:</strong> NPR 2,00,000 — 50% upfront, 50% on delivery</li>
            <li><strong>Business Website:</strong> NPR 6,50,000 — 50% upfront, 50% on delivery</li>
            <li><strong>Web Application:</strong> NPR 13,00,000+ — Milestone-based payments</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="leading-relaxed mt-4">All prices are in Nepalese Rupees (NPR). Payment is due within 7 days of invoice. Late payments incur a 2% monthly fee.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">3. Project Scope</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">Project scope is defined in the initial proposal and statement of work. Any changes to scope may result in additional charges. We will notify you before proceeding with scope changes.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">4. Revisions</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Landing Page:</strong> 2 rounds of revisions included</li>
            <li><strong>Business Website:</strong> 3 rounds of revisions included</li>
            <li><strong>Web Application:</strong> 4 rounds of revisions included</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="leading-relaxed mt-4">Additional revisions are billed at NPR 5,000 per round.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">Upon full payment, you receive full ownership of the delivered website, app, or software. We retain the right to showcase the work in our portfolio unless you request otherwise in writing.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">6. Support Period</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Landing Page:</strong> 7 days post-launch support</li>
            <li><strong>Business Website:</strong> 30 days post-launch support</li>
            <li><strong>Web Application:</strong> 90 days post-launch support</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="leading-relaxed mt-4">Extended support available via monthly maintenance plans starting at NPR 35,000/month.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">7. Cancellation</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">You may cancel at any time. Payment is due for all work completed up to the cancellation date. Milestone-based payments ensure you only pay for delivered work.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">ROOKIE STUDIO's total liability shall not exceed the total amount paid for the project. We are not liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-text mb-4">9. Contact</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">For questions about these terms, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@rookiestudio.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">hello@rookiestudio.com</a></p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
